      "text": "（あかん……まだ一限やのに眠過ぎる……久しぶりの）\n（オフやからって調子に乗って夜更かしし過ぎたわ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（This is bad… it's only the first period and I'm so sleepy…）\n（I stayed up too late playing games just because it was my day off…）",
