      "text": "（どうすればトリエルがもっと飛躍出来るんか）\n（考え出したら眠れんように……ふわぁ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Once I started thinking about how TRINITYAiLE could soar higher‚）\n（I couldn't get to sleep… Yawn…）",
        "id": ""
