      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_05-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "（そろそろテストも近いし、居眠りは命取りや）\n（習ったことはその場で覚えていきたい……でも……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Exams are coming up soon‚ so nodding off is a death sentence.）\n（I want to memorize things as I learn them… but…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.6890483976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
