      "text": "（こういう時はまず、手の甲をつねって……ほっぺも）\n（つねって……先生の発言をとりあえず全部メモ……っと）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（In times like this‚ first‚ pinch the back of your hand… and your cheek.）\n（Pinch… and take notes on everything the teacher says for now.）",
        "id": ""
