      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.21
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_05-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "（ふむふむ……なるほど「……時は幕末、強い信念を持ち）\n（動乱の幕末を駆け抜けた新選組達は……」）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Hmm‚ hmm… I see. \"…During the Bakumatsu era‚ with strong convictions‚）\n（the Shinsengumi who charged through the turbulent era…\"）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.9186172922,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_05-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "（待って！？　何これ！？　めちゃめちゃ熱いやん！）\n（新選組が好きなオタクは多いと聞いてはいました）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Wait a second!? What is this?! This is incredibly intense!）\n（I heard there are many otakus who love the Shinsengumi‚）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.2504318039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.7837192019
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_05-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、ここまでとは……）\n（もっとはよう知りたかったわ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（but I didn't know it was to this extent…）\n（I wish I had known about this sooner…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.7837192019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_05-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "（『誠』の旗を掲げ生き抜いた隊士達の関係性や）\n（人間ドラマなんて、『もんバケ』にも勝るとも劣らない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The relationships of the soldiers who lived under the banner of 'Sincerity'‚）\n（and the human drama are just as amazing as \"Mon-Bake\"!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.3205221613,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.8488672693
    },
    {
