      "text": "（「薬売りの少年だった土方が、武士になる夢を掲げた）\n（近藤のため鬼の副長へと変貌していく……」はぁ、無理）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（\"Hijikata‚ who was a medicine peddler boy‚ becomes the 'Demon Vice-Commander'）\n（to support Kondo's dream of becoming a samurai…\" Sigh‚ I can't even.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.8488672693,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.6122005264
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_05-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "（「近藤のことを慕う一番隊組長の沖田総司は……」）\n（なんや、なんや……土方と沖田で近藤を取り合うんか？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（\"Okita Souji‚ the captain of the first unit who admires Kondo…\"）\n（What's this‚ what's this… Are Hijikata and Okita fighting over Kondo?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.6122005264,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.9592071016
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
