      "text": "（他にも気になる隊士がようけおるけど……ん？　んん？）\n（「新選組についてはこれくらいで次のページへ」？　）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（There are so many other members I'm curious about… Wait? Huh?）\n（\"That's all for the Shinsengumi‚ moving on to the next page\"?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.9592071016,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_05-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "（「気になった人は自分で調べて下さい……」？）\n（アニメの予告ちゃうねんから！　引きはいらんねん！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（\"If you're curious‚ please look it up yourself…\"?）\n（This isn't an anime teaser! Don't leave me on a cliffhanger!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.707869033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.8861683328
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_05-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "（先生！　なんでいいとこで切るんや！）\n（そこ、はしょらんともっと教えて下さい！　彼らのこと）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Teacher! Why are you cutting it off at the best part?!）\n（Don't skip that part‚ tell me more! About them!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.8861683328,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.5039913932
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_05-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "（はぁ～これはえらいこっちゃやわ。寝てる暇なんて）\n（あらへん。もう眠気なんてどっかにいってもうた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Sigh~ This is big. There's no time to be sleeping.）\n（My sleepiness has already completely vanished.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.5039913932,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_05-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "（はっ！　そうや！　ひらめいたで！）\n（トリエルがもっともっと飛躍するために必要なものが）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Wait! I've got it! I just had a brilliant idea!）\n（What TRINITYAiLE needs to soar even higher is…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.4015194375,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158.8495872616
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_yu_01_05-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "（うちが鬼の副リーダー鈴村優になって）\n（トリエルのリーダーである天動瑠依を支えんねん！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Me becoming the 'Demon Vice-Leader' Yu Suzumura‚）\n（and supporting TRINITYAiLE's leader‚ Rui Tendo!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.8495872616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 166.7562632362
